<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru" data-lang="ru">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Дмитрий Парамонов — DevOps Team Lead</title>
<meta name="description" content="Дмитрий Парамонов — DevOps Team Lead. 20+ лет в IT, 9+ лет в DevOps/SRE, финтех, Kubernetes, CI/CD, DevSecOps.">
<meta property="og:title" content="Дмитрий Парамонов — DevOps Team Lead">
<meta property="og:description" content="20+ лет в IT · DevOps/SRE · Kubernetes · CI/CD · DevSecOps · Санкт-Петербург / ОАЭ">
<meta property="og:type" content="website">
<link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><rect width=%22100%22 height=%22100%22 rx=%2220%22 fill=%22%230a0f0d%22/><text x=%2250%22 y=%2268%22 font-size=%2258%22 fill=%22%2300ff9c%22 font-family=%22monospace%22 text-anchor=%22middle%22>&gt;_</text></svg>">
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#0a0f0d;
  --bg-2:#0e1512;
  --panel:#111a16;
  --line:#1e2c26;
  --text:#d7e6df;
  --muted:#7f978c;
  --accent:#00ff9c;
  --accent-dim:#0a5c3f;
  --amber:#ffb454;
  --danger:#ff6b6b;
  --mono: "JetBrains Mono","SF Mono",ui-monospace,Menlo,Consolas,monospace;
  --sans: "Inter","Segoe UI",system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;
  --radius:10px;
  --maxw:960px;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;}
html,body{margin:0;padding:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--sans);scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{overflow-x:hidden;line-height:1.55;position:relative;}
a{color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none;}
a:hover{text-decoration:underline;}
:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--accent);outline-offset:2px;border-radius:4px;}
img{max-width:100%;display:block;}

/* circuit-grid backdrop */
body::before{
  content:"";position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;pointer-events:none;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(0,255,156,.05) 1px,transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(0,255,156,.05) 1px,transparent 1px);
  background-size:42px 42px;
  mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 55% at 50% 0%,#000 0%,transparent 75%);
}
/* scanline / vignette texture */
body::after{
  content:"";position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:90;pointer-events:none;
  background:repeating-linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(255,255,255,.018) 0px,rgba(255,255,255,.018) 1px,transparent 1px,transparent 3px),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 90% 70% at 50% 0%,transparent 55%,rgba(0,0,0,.55) 100%);
}

.grad-text{background:linear-gradient(100deg,var(--accent) 0%,#5ad1ff 45%,#7a8cff 100%);-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent;}
.blink{display:inline-block;width:.55em;background:var(--accent);animation:blink 1s steps(1) infinite;}
@keyframes blink{50%{opacity:0;}}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){ .blink{animation:none;opacity:1;} }

/* language toggling */
[data-lang-content]{display:none;}
html[data-lang="ru"] [data-lang-content="ru"]{display:block;}
html[data-lang="en"] [data-lang-content="en"]{display:block;}
html[data-lang="ru"] span[data-lang-content="ru"],
html[data-lang="en"] span[data-lang-content="en"]{display:inline;}

/* scroll progress bar */
#progress{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;height:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent),var(--amber));width:0%;z-index:100;transition:width .1s linear;}

/* ambient orbs */
.orb{position:fixed;border-radius:50%;filter:blur(60px);opacity:.25;z-index:0;pointer-events:none;}
.orb-a{width:420px;height:420px;background:var(--accent);top:-120px;left:-120px;animation:float1 22s ease-in-out infinite;}
.orb-b{width:360px;height:360px;background:#3a6cff;bottom:-100px;right:-100px;animation:float2 26s ease-in-out infinite;}
@keyframes float1{0%,100%{transform:translate(0,0);}50%{transform:translate(60px,80px);}}
@keyframes float2{0%,100%{transform:translate(0,0);}50%{transform:translate(-60px,-60px);}}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
  .orb{animation:none;}
  *{scroll-behavior:auto !important;}
}

/* topbar */
header.top{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;backdrop-filter:blur(10px);background:rgba(10,15,13,.75);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}
.top-inner{max-width:var(--maxw);margin:0 auto;padding:12px 20px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:12px;}
.brand{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);}
.brand b{color:var(--accent);}
.lang-switch{display:flex;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;}
.lang-switch button{background:transparent;border:none;color:var(--muted);padding:6px 10px;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;}
.lang-switch button[aria-pressed="true"]{background:var(--accent-dim);color:var(--accent);}

main{max-width:var(--maxw);margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px;position:relative;z-index:1;}

/* terminal window chrome around hero */
.terminal{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--panel),var(--bg-2));box-shadow:0 30px 80px -30px rgba(0,255,156,.12), inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.02);overflow:hidden;margin:36px 0;position:relative;}
.terminal::before{content:"";position:absolute;inset:-1px;border-radius:14px;padding:1px;background:linear-gradient(120deg,rgba(0,255,156,.35),transparent 30%,transparent 70%,rgba(122,140,255,.35));-webkit-mask:linear-gradient(#000 0 0) content-box,linear-gradient(#000 0 0);-webkit-mask-composite:xor;mask-composite:exclude;pointer-events:none;}
.term-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);background:rgba(255,255,255,.015);}
.term-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;}
.term-dot.r{background:#ff6b6b;}
.term-dot.y{background:#ffb454;}
.term-dot.g{background:#00ff9c;}
.term-title{margin-left:6px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);}
.term-body{padding:36px 28px 32px;}
.term-line{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:14px;min-height:16px;white-space:pre-wrap;line-height:1.7;}
.term-line .prompt{color:var(--accent);}
.term-line .out{color:var(--text);}

/* hero */
.hero{padding:0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:120px 1fr;gap:28px;align-items:start;}
@media (max-width:640px){.hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;text-align:center;}}
.photo-wrap{width:120px;height:120px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--line);box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(0,255,156,.06), 0 0 30px -6px rgba(0,255,156,.5);transform-style:preserve-3d;transition:transform .15s ease;margin:0 auto;position:relative;}
.photo-wrap img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;}
.photo-ring{position:absolute;inset:-6px;border-radius:20px;border:1px dashed rgba(0,255,156,.35);animation:spin 16s linear infinite;}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg);}}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){.photo-ring{animation:none;}}

/* CI/CD pipeline strip */
.pipeline{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0;margin:26px 0 6px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);position:relative;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.pipeline .stage{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;padding:7px 12px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:20px;background:var(--panel);position:relative;z-index:1;}
.pipeline .stage .led{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 6px var(--accent);}
.pipeline .arrow{width:22px;height:1px;background:var(--line);position:relative;overflow:visible;}
.pipeline .arrow::after{content:"";position:absolute;top:-2px;left:0;width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 8px var(--accent);animation:runner 3.2s linear infinite;}
.pipeline .arrow:nth-of-type(2)::after{animation-delay:0s;}
@keyframes runner{0%{left:0;opacity:0;}10%{opacity:1;}90%{opacity:1;}100%{left:100%;opacity:0;}}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){.pipeline .arrow::after{animation:none;opacity:0;}}
@media (max-width:640px){.pipeline{justify-content:center;}}
.status-line{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:.06em;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.status-line .dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 8px var(--accent);animation:pulse 2s infinite;}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1;}50%{opacity:.35;}}
.status-alert{font-weight:800;animation:alertBlink 1s steps(2,jump-none) infinite;padding:1px 6px;border-radius:4px;}
@keyframes alertBlink{
  0%,49%{color:#ff3b3b;background:rgba(255,59,59,.12);text-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(255,59,59,.85);}
  50%,100%{color:#ffffff;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);text-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(255,255,255,.85);}
}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
  .status-alert{animation:none;color:#ff3b3b;}
}
.loc{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:14px;}
h1{font-size:clamp(30px,5.5vw,46px);margin:0 0 4px;letter-spacing:-.01em;font-weight:800;}
.role{font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 20px;font-family:var(--mono);}
.stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:10px;margin:20px 0 22px;}
@media (max-width:640px){.stats{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}}
.stat{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:12px 10px;background:var(--panel);text-align:center;transition:.2s;}
.stat:hover{border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 24px -8px rgba(0,255,156,.45);transform:translateY(-2px);}
.stat .num{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:24px;color:var(--accent);font-weight:700;}
.stat .label{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px;}
.cta-row{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
@media (max-width:640px){.cta-row{justify-content:center;}}
.btn{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--text);background:var(--panel);cursor:pointer;transition:.15s;}
.btn:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none;}
.btn.primary{background:var(--accent-dim);border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);}

/* section headers */
.eyebrow{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:.08em;margin:0 0 6px;}
section{padding:44px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line);}
h2{font-size:22px;margin:0 0 18px;}

/* about */
.about-text{max-width:700px;color:var(--text);}
.values{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:12px;margin-top:22px;}
@media (max-width:760px){.values{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}}
.value{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:14px;background:var(--panel);}
.value b{color:var(--accent);display:block;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;margin-bottom:6px;}
.value p{margin:0;font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);}

/* timeline — git-log graph rail */
.timeline-rail{position:relative;padding-left:26px;}
.timeline-rail::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:5px;top:8px;bottom:8px;width:1px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--accent),var(--line) 12%,var(--line) 88%,transparent);}
.job{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--panel);margin-bottom:10px;overflow:hidden;position:relative;}
.job::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:-25px;top:20px;width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--bg);border:2px solid var(--muted);z-index:1;}
.job.current::before{border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 10px var(--accent);}
.job summary{list-style:none;cursor:pointer;padding:14px 16px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;transition:background .15s;}
.job summary:hover{background:rgba(0,255,156,.03);}
.job summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none;}
.job summary .role-title{font-weight:600;font-size:15px;}
.job summary .company{color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;}
.job summary .dates{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--accent);white-space:nowrap;}
.job[open] summary{border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}
.job .body{padding:14px 16px;font-size:14px;color:var(--text);}
.job .body ul{margin:8px 0 0;padding-left:18px;}
.job .body li{margin-bottom:4px;}
.job .toolset{margin-top:10px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);}
.present-badge{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;background:var(--accent-dim);color:var(--accent);padding:2px 7px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:6px;}

/* skills layout with decorative visual filling empty space */
.skills-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:20px;}
@media (min-width:860px){
  .skills-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr 240px;align-items:start;}
  .skills-visual{position:sticky;top:90px;}
}
.skills-visual{display:none;}
@media (min-width:860px){ .skills-visual{display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;height:340px;} }

.sphere-wrap{width:220px;height:220px;perspective:900px;position:relative;}
.sphere-wrap::before{content:"";position:absolute;inset:10px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%,rgba(0,255,156,.16),transparent 70%);filter:blur(2px);}
.sphere{width:100%;height:100%;position:relative;transform-style:preserve-3d;animation:sphereSpin 14s linear infinite;}
.sphere .ring{position:absolute;inset:0;border:1px solid rgba(0,255,156,.32);border-radius:50%;box-shadow:0 0 14px -4px rgba(0,255,156,.35) inset;}
.sphere .ring.rx1{transform:rotateX(0deg);}
.sphere .ring.rx2{transform:rotateX(30deg);}
.sphere .ring.rx3{transform:rotateX(60deg);}
.sphere .ring.rx4{transform:rotateX(90deg);border-color:rgba(122,140,255,.4);}
.sphere .ring.rx5{transform:rotateX(120deg);}
.sphere .ring.rx6{transform:rotateX(150deg);}
.sphere .ring.ry1{transform:rotateY(60deg);}
.sphere .ring.ry2{transform:rotateY(120deg);}
.sphere .core{position:absolute;inset:38%;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);opacity:.5;filter:blur(6px);}
.sphere .sat{position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:#5ad1ff;box-shadow:0 0 10px #5ad1ff;transform:translate(-50%,-50%) rotateY(0deg) translateX(120px);animation:satOrbit 6s linear infinite;}
@keyframes sphereSpin{from{transform:rotateY(0deg) rotateX(8deg);}to{transform:rotateY(360deg) rotateX(8deg);}}
@keyframes satOrbit{from{transform:translate(-50%,-50%) rotateY(0deg) translateX(120px);}to{transform:translate(-50%,-50%) rotateY(360deg) translateX(120px);}}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
  .sphere{animation:none;}
  .sphere .sat{animation:none;}
}

/* skills */
.skill-group{margin-bottom:16px;}
.skill-group h3{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:.06em;margin:0 0 8px;text-transform:uppercase;}
.tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:7px;}
.tag{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:20px;padding:4px 10px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text);background:var(--bg-2);transition:.15s;}
.tag:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 12px -3px rgba(0,255,156,.5);}

/* contact */
.contact-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:10px;}
@media (max-width:640px){.contact-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
.contact-card{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:12px 14px;background:var(--panel);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;font-size:13px;}
.contact-card .k{font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--muted);font-size:11px;}
.copy-btn{background:none;border:none;color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;font-size:12px;}
.copy-btn:hover{color:var(--accent);}

footer{border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding:24px 0 40px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;align-items:center;}
footer a{color:var(--muted);}
#visits-badge{height:20px;opacity:.85;}

.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px);transition:opacity .5s ease, transform .5s ease;}
.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="progress"></div>
<div class="orb orb-a"></div>
<div class="orb orb-b"></div>

<header class="top">
  <div class="top-inner">
    <div class="brand">&gt;_ <b>forestplus/TopDevOps</b></div>
    <div class="lang-switch" role="group" aria-label="Language / Язык">
      <button id="btn-ru" aria-pressed="true" onclick="setLang('ru')">RU</button>
      <button id="btn-en" aria-pressed="false" onclick="setLang('en')">EN</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="terminal" style="margin-top:28px;">
    <div class="term-bar">
      <span class="term-dot r"></span><span class="term-dot y"></span><span class="term-dot g"></span>
      <span class="term-title">dmitry@devops — zsh — 96×24</span>
    </div>
    <div class="term-body">
      <div class="term-line"><span class="prompt">$</span> <span id="typed-line" class="out"></span><span class="blink">&nbsp;</span></div>

      <section class="hero">
        <div class="photo-wrap" id="tilt-card">
          <div class="photo-ring"></div>
          <img src="assets/dmitry.png" alt="Дмитрий Парамонов" width="120" height="120" loading="eager">
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="status-line">
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <span data-lang-content="ru">СИСТЕМА: НА СВЯЗИ · <span class="status-alert">ОТКРЫТ К ПРЕДЛОЖЕНИЯМ</span></span>
            <span data-lang-content="en">STATUS: ONLINE · <span class="status-alert">OPEN TO OFFERS</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="loc">
            <span data-lang-content="ru">Санкт-Петербург · открыт к переезду и удалёнке · РФ / ОАЭ</span>
            <span data-lang-content="en">Saint Petersburg, Russia · open to relocation &amp; remote · RU / UAE work authorization</span>
          </div>
          <h1><span class="grad-text">Дмитрий Парамонов</span></h1>
          <p class="role">DevOps Team Lead</p>

          <div class="stats">
            <div class="stat"><div class="num" data-count="20" data-suffix="+">0</div>
              <div class="label"><span data-lang-content="ru">лет опыта в IT</span><span data-lang-content="en">years in IT</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat"><div class="num" data-count="250" data-suffix="+">0</div>
              <div class="label"><span data-lang-content="ru">серверов под управлением</span><span data-lang-content="en">servers managed</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat"><div class="num" data-count="11" data-suffix="">0</div>
              <div class="label"><span data-lang-content="ru">этапов карьеры</span><span data-lang-content="en">career stages</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat"><div class="num" data-count="9" data-suffix="+">0</div>
              <div class="label"><span data-lang-content="ru">лет в DevOps/SRE</span><span data-lang-content="en">years in DevOps/SRE</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="pipeline" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="stage"><span class="led"></span>BUILD</div>
            <div class="arrow"></div>
            <div class="stage"><span class="led"></span>TEST</div>
            <div class="arrow"></div>
            <div class="stage"><span class="led"></span>DEPLOY</div>
            <div class="arrow"></div>
            <div class="stage"><span class="led"></span>MONITOR</div>
          </div>

          <div class="cta-row" style="margin-top:20px;">
            <a class="btn primary" data-lang-content="ru" href="resume.pdf">⬇ Скачать резюме (RU)</a>
            <a class="btn primary" data-lang-content="en" href="resume_en.pdf">⬇ Download resume (EN)</a>
            <a class="btn" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/topdevops" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <span data-lang-content="ru">LinkedIn →</span><span data-lang-content="en">LinkedIn →</span>
            </a>
            <a class="btn" href="https://t.me/TopDevOps" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Telegram →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="reveal">
    <p class="eyebrow" data-lang-content="ru">кто_я</p>
    <p class="eyebrow" data-lang-content="en">about_me</p>
    <h2 data-lang-content="ru">О себе</h2>
    <h2 data-lang-content="en">About</h2>
    <p class="about-text" data-lang-content="ru">
      Прошёл путь от инженера технической поддержки до CEO и CIO. Последние 9+ лет полностью сфокусирован на DevOps-методологии: контейнеризация приложений на Docker с оркестрацией в Kubernetes и OpenShift, преимущественно в финтех-проектах. Строю production-инфраструктуру с минимальным time-to-market и внедряю практики DevSecOps для повышения надёжности систем. Открыт к интересным проектам и долгосрочному сотрудничеству — удалённо, гибридно или на месте, в России и ОАЭ.
    </p>
    <p class="about-text" data-lang-content="en">
      I've gone from technical support engineer to business co-owner and CEO/CIO. For the past 9+ years I've been fully focused on DevOps practices: containerizing applications with Docker and orchestrating them on Kubernetes and OpenShift, mainly in fintech projects. I build production infrastructure with minimal time-to-market and apply DevSecOps practices to improve system reliability. Open to interesting projects and long-term collaboration — remote, hybrid, or on-site, in Russia and the UAE.
    </p>

    <div class="values">
      <div class="value">
        <b data-lang-content="ru">Надёжность</b><b data-lang-content="en">Reliability</b>
        <p data-lang-content="ru">Проектирую инфраструктуру так, чтобы инциденты решались быстро, а не повторялись.</p>
        <p data-lang-content="en">I design infrastructure so incidents get resolved fast — and don't repeat.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value">
        <b data-lang-content="ru">Скорость</b><b data-lang-content="en">Speed</b>
        <p data-lang-content="ru">Выстраиваю CI/CD и автоматизацию, которые сокращают time-to-market.</p>
        <p data-lang-content="en">I build CI/CD and automation that cut time-to-market.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value">
        <b data-lang-content="ru">Люди</b><b data-lang-content="en">People</b>
        <p data-lang-content="ru">Нанимаю, обучаю и выращиваю сильные DevOps-команды.</p>
        <p data-lang-content="en">I hire, train, and grow strong DevOps teams.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value">
        <b data-lang-content="ru">Безопасность</b><b data-lang-content="en">Security</b>
        <p data-lang-content="ru">Внедряю DevSecOps как часть процесса, а не отдельный этап.</p>
        <p data-lang-content="en">I build DevSecOps into the process, not as a bolt-on step.</p>
      </div>
